snippet.title: Journey to The Center of The Earth gameplay (PC Game, 1988)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Journey to The Center of The Earth, Dos PC game produced by Chip in 1988 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/journey-to-the-center-of-the-earth/7018/
Journey to The Center of The Earth is an interesting difficult /strategy/action game. You play the role of a scientist, trying to reach the center of the earth.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
